snippet.title: Geek Out For A Minute
snippet.description:
Welcome to "Geek Out For A Minute" where we talk about all things relating to comics, video games or well anything that we can geek out on. From Marvel Comics, DC Comics, Transformers, Star Wars, etc. 

Any questions you'd like to address us or a topic you would like for us to cover contact us to our various media.

Twitter: @letsgeekout1
E-mail:   letsgeekoutforamin@gmail.com

Also follow us on facebook: http://facebook.com/geekout1min

Don't forget to share, discuss and spread the word!
